flowchart TD
  Start[Start Calibration] --> Project[Project 4 Corner Targets]
  Project --> Tap[User Taps Each Target]
  Tap --> Capture[Capture Camera-Space Points]
  Capture --> Solve[Solve Homography]
  Solve --> Save[Save to calibration.yaml]
  Save --> Validate[Validate: Project Grid]
  Validate --> Check{Error OK?}
  Check -->|Yes| Done[Calibration Done]
  Check -->|No| Retry[Suggest Recalibrate]
  Retry --> Project
